description:
A major incident in peaceful Skyland?! The infant princess http://anidb.net/ch129478 [Elle-chan] has been kidnapped by a monster from the Undergu Empire! A brave girl named http://anidb.net/ch129481 [Sora] follows the princess into a strange hole. It leads her to another world called Sorashido City.
Televisions? Bicycles? Are these magical devices?!?! There`s no time to be surprised! Sora has to take the princess back to the castle as soon as possible! Flying between two worlds! This is the beginning of a Precure adventure! It`s hero time!
Source: Crunchyroll

REGULAR.description:
The infant princess Ellee-chan has been kidnapped by a monster! 
A brave girl named Sora follows the kidnapper into a strange hole to save the princess, but when she finds a way out, she’s in another world?!
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: I`m a Hero Girl?! Cure Sky to the Rescue!
Watashi ga Hero Girl!? Cure Sky Sanjou!!
わたしがヒーローガール!? キュアスカイ参上!!

REGULAR.description:
After defeating Ranborg, Mashiro takes Sora back to her home. Mashiro’s grandmother Yoyo does not appear surprised by their arrival and welcomes Sora and Ellee.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: A Hero in the House?!
Hero ga Ouchi ni Yatte Kita!?
ヒーローがおうちにやってきた!?

REGULAR.description:
Ellee is in a bad mood. Sora and the others realize this is because she misses her Papa and Mama, so they decide to use the Mirror Pad to communicate with Skyland.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Hic-hic-homesick! Don`t Cry Ellee-chan!
Shikushiku Homesick! Nakanaide Ellee-chan!
シクシクホームシック! 泣かないでエルちゃん!

REGULAR.description:
Kabaton sets a sneaky trap for Mashiro and the others. Sora’s Mirage Pen is stolen by Kabaton and she’s no longer able to transform into Cure Sky.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: I`m a Hero Girl Too! Cure Prism`s Arrival!
Watashi mo Hero Girl! Cure Prism Toujou!!
わたしもヒーローガール! キュアプリズム登場!!

REGULAR.description:
Sora dreams that Prism is attacked by Ranborg. Tortured by her thoughts, Sora tells Mashiro, “I don’t want you to transform into a Precure” and tries to protect Ellee all by herself.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Hand in Hand! Our New Attack!
Te to Te o Tsunaide! Watashitachi no Atarashii Waza!
手と手をつないで! 私たちの新しい技!

REGULAR.description:
The new semester has begun, and Mashiro heads to school, but Sora can’t enter. While out on errands, Sora runs into Ageha, who guesses that she’s lonely because she’s not with Mashiro.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Tell Me! Sora`s True Feelings
Tsutaete! Sora no Hontou no Kimochi
伝えて! ソラの本当の気持ち

REGULAR.description:
Sora is enrolled in the same school as Mashiro. However, she is worried she’ll accidentally tell everyone she’s from Skyland, so she tries not to stand out at school, but…
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Dokidoki! Tenkousei wa Hero Girl!!
Thrilling! The Transfer Student Is a Hero Girl!
ドキドキ! 転校生はヒーローガール!!

REGULAR.description:
A strange boy enters the room and speaks to Ellee. It turns out he’s a boy named Tsubasa, a member of the Puni Bird Tribe. What is Tsubasa’s reason for not going home to Skyland?
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: The Flightless Bird and the Strange Boy
Tobenai Tori to, Fushigi na Shounen
飛べない鳥と, ふしぎな少年

REGULAR.description:
As the saucer-shaped Ranborg rampages above, Ellee is worried and flies out of the house to find Sky and Prism. Tsubasa chases after Ellee to protect her, but winds up getting captured by Ranborg
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Wings of Courage, Fly Cure Wing!
Yuuki no Tsubasa, Tobe Cure Wing!!
勇気の翼, 飛べキュアウィング!!

REGULAR.description:
Sora and the others arrange a welcome party for Tsubasa. He says he wants to eat a dish from Skyland called “yakitai” but they struggle to make it taste like the original.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Mumumu! Omoide no Ryouritte Donna Aji!?
Yum! What`s the Taste of Home?
むむむ! 思い出の料理ってどんな味!?

REGULAR.description:
Ageha invites everyone on a trip to the mountains. They arrive at Mount Raso and join in a riddle-solving game, but Tsubasa is on the same team as Ageha and finds himself getting irritated by her antics…
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Awkward Pair!? Tsubasa and Ageha
Kimazui Futari!? Tsubasa to Ageha
気まずい二人!? ツバサとあげは
Tough! Cure Sky vs. Kabaton
Tsueeee! Cure Sky tai Kabaton!!
ツエェェェ! キュアスカイ対カバトン!!

REGULAR.description:
Sora and the others go to buy Ellee her first pair of shoes, and a lady lets them buy the ones she was planning on purchasing. Meanwhile, Yoyo succeeds in opening the tunnel to Skyland.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Deliver It! First Present
Todokete! Hajimete no Okurimono
届けて! はじめてのおくりもの

REGULAR.description:
Sora returns to Skyland and reunites with Captain Shalala, the captain of the Azure Guards and the person she admires most, and becomes an apprentice member of the Guards. However, one of the apprentices doubts Sora’s skill.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Skyland e! Akogare no Ano Hito to no Saikai
To Skyland! Reunited with the Person She Admires!
スカイランドへ! 憧れのあの人との再会

REGULAR.description:
Skyland is continually attacked by Ranborgs. Sora and the Azure Guards defeat them, but Battamonda collects their energy and puts Skyland into a crisis.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: A Mega Ranborg Explosion? Protect Skyland!
Chou Kyodai Ranborg Dai Bakuhatsu!? Mamore Skyland!
超巨大ランボーグ大爆発!? 守れスカイランド!

REGULAR.description:
Sora and the gang return to Sorashido City to see Yoyo. The King and Queen are under a curse, and Ellee is feeling sad. Ageha proposes a Puppet Play to cheer her up.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Elleetarou Ichiza no Oni Taiji
The Elleetaro Squad Defeats the Ogre!
えるたろう一座のおに退治
The Great Baton Pass! Mashiro`s Intense Relay
Watase Saikou no Baton! Mashiro Honki no Relay
わたせ最高のバトン! ましろ本気のリレー

REGULAR.description:
During her practicum at the nursery school, the children find out Ageha is friends with the Precures. But one of the children, Takeru, disagrees on what it is to be a Precure, and runs outside.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Ageage! Saikyou no Hoikushi Cure Butterfly!!
Exciting! The Best Nursery School Teacher, Cure Butterfly!
アゲアゲ! 最強の保育士キュアバタフライ!!

REGULAR.description:
Ageha begins living at Mashiro’s house and makes herself busy cooking and cleaning for Sora and the gang. Tsubasa worries Ageha is wearing herself out, and Ageha makes a special request to Tsubasa.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Ageha and Tsubasa Get Colorfully Excited!
Ageha to Tsubasa, Colorful ni Ageteko!
あげはとツバサ, カラフルにアゲてこ!

REGULAR.description:
Ageha’s co-worker and art school student Natsumi suggests that Mashiro enters the “Everyone’s Picture Book” contest. Sora and the gang encourage her, and she decides to try making a picture book.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Mashiro no Yume: Saisho no Ippo
The First Step Towards Mashiro`s Dream
ましろの夢 最初の一歩

REGULAR.description:
Yoyo invites everyone on an outing to the mountain highlands. There, Yoyo has a vegetable garden growing, and Tsubasa is surprised at how much Yoyo knows about vegetables.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Hirogare! Chishiki no Tsubasa
Soar! Wings of Knowledge
ひろがれ! 知識の翼

REGULAR.description:
In Skyland, many people are spotting a woman in a blue cape, just like Captain Shalala. While out shopping with everyone, Sora spots a woman in a blue cape too and chases after her.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Battamonda Saigo no Hisaku!
Battamonda`s Final Strategy
バッタモンダー最後の秘策!

REGULAR.description:
A discouraged Sora returns to Skyland and reunites with her family. Meanwhile, the Ranborg containing Captain Shalala appears in Sorashido City. Mashiro and the others take it on without Sora.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Broken Dreams and Renewed Strength!
Kudaketa Yume to, Yomigaeru Chikara
砕けた夢と, よみがえる力
Kagayaku Ichibanboshi Ellee-chan no Himitsu
Sparkling Morning Star, Ellee-chan`s Secret
輝く一番星☆エルちゃんの秘密

REGULAR.description:
After being asked by the King and Queen to care for Ellee, Sora and the others return with her to Sorashido City, where they visit Sorashido Nature Park to see the animals. However, they also encounter a new underling from the Undergu Empire.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Fun! The Princess Goes to the Zoo!
Wakuwaku! Princess, Doubutsuen ni Iku!
ワクワク! プリンセス, 動物園に行く!

REGULAR.description:
Mashiro’s parents are finally returning from overseas for a visit, so Sora and the gang go to the airport to pick them up. While exploring the airport, they meet a girl named Shoko who knows a lot about airplanes.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Take Off! Hikouki de Tsunagaru Omoi
Take Off! Memories Connected by Airplanes
テイクオフ! 飛行機でつながる想い

REGULAR.description:
Sora and the gang get sucked into the Mirror Pad by a vortex. Inside the Mirror Pad is a special stage where they are made to do “special training.”
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: A Wild Lesson in the Mirror Pad?!
Mirror Pad de Wakuwaku Lesson!?
ミラーパッドでワクワクレッスン!?
Ageha no Ageage Fashion Show
Ageha`s Exciting Fashion Show!
あげはのアゲアゲファッションショー

REGULAR.description:
In an abandoned European-style house at the edge of town, Sora is surprised when a stuffed animal talks to her. Although Sora is scared when it follows her home, she begins to feel like there is some reason for the situation and decides to help.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Sora and the Missing Stuffed Animal
Sora to, Wasurerareta Nuigurumi
ソラと, 忘れられたぬいぐるみ

REGULAR.description:
To wrap up their summer holiday, everyone goes to the beach, but Sora doesn’t know how to swim and she nearly drowns. Everyone tries to teach her how to swim but she has trouble getting the hang of it, until…
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Hirogaru Umi! Beach Paradise!
Soaring Sea! Beach Paradise
ひろがる海! ビーチパラダイス!

REGULAR.description:
In order to improve Ellee’s mood, Sora and the gang visit the Sorashido Photo Studio. Everyone enjoys the photo shoot, but on the way home a strange man in a black hooded cloak appears and takes Ellee.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: A New Threat! Rescue Ellee-chan!
Arata na Kyoui! Ellee-chan o Torimodose!
新たな脅威! エルちゃんを取り戻せ!

REGULAR.description:
Ellee says she is Cure Majesty, but she still can’t transform at will. Meanwhile, Minoton 
re-appears, but this time he has been brainwashed with Undergu Energy.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Big Transformation! Cure Majesty!
Dai Henshin! Cure Majesty!!
大変身! キュアマジェスティ!!

REGULAR.description:
Yoyo summons Sora and the gang to Skyland, where they explore a ruin that suddenly appeared. In the depths is a book called “Majectic Chroniclon” that contains the Ultimate Power.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Kyuukyoku no Chikara! Majestic Chroniclon
Ultimate Power! Majestic Chroniclon
究極のちから! マジェスティクルニクルン

REGULAR.description:
After losing to the Precures, Battamonda is now living in Sorashido City, calling himself “Monda.” He disguises himself as an art school student, and approaches Mashiro, who has lost her confidence…
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Mon-mon! Mashiro and His Return!
Monmon! Mashiro to Kaette Kita Aitsu
もんもん! ましろと帰ってきたアイツ

REGULAR.description:
While the ace of the girls’ baseball team, Tamaki Shinomiya, is on rest due to an elbow injury, Sora is asked to be their coach. Then, they find out that Tamaki will need surgery
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Import Player Sora! Ace and Hero
Suketto Sora! Ace to Hero
助っ人ソラ! エースとヒーロー

REGULAR.description:
Takeru, the boy who Ageha has become friends with at the nursery school where she’s training, is moving away. Takeru is sad and doesn’t want to play with the other children, and Ageha doesn’t know what to do.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Ageha Fails at Being the Best Nursery School Teacher?
Ageha, Saikyou no Hoikushi Shikkaku!?
あげは, 最強の保育士失格!?

REGULAR.description:
Sora and the gang look at photos from when Mashiro and Ageha first met, and decide to visit the place in the photo. However, no matter how they walk around the neighborhood, they can’t find the tree from the picture.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Futari wa Nakyaoshi: Omoide no Ki!
Two Friends! The Tree of Memories
ふたりは仲良し♡思い出の木!

REGULAR.description:
The Bright Jewel that shines in the night sky of Skyland suddenly goes dark. Sora and the gang travel to Floating Island where it is located to try to find the cause.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Oozora o Sukue! Ukishima no Himitsu
Save the Sky! The Secret of Floating Island
大空を救え! 浮き島のひみつ

REGULAR.description:
For Halloween, Sora and the gang decorate Mashiro’s house like a witch’s house, and welcome children. Meanwhile, Cure Pumpkin appears in town, saying he’s a member of the Precures..
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Dai Majo Yoyo to Halloween Party!
Great Witch Yoyo and the Halloween Party!
大魔女ヨヨとハロウィンパーティー!

REGULAR.description:
Ellee suddenly says “I will marry Tsubasa!” For Ellee’s sake everyone puts on a play wedding, but even after the playing is over, Ellee doesn’t let go of Tsubasa’s hand.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Good Fwiends! Ellee`s Wedding!
Nakayochi: Ellee-chan Kekkonshiki
なかよち♡エルちゃん結婚式☆

REGULAR.description:
Mashiro is preparing to enter a picture book contest once more. While working on new ideas at Sorashido Park, Monda talks to her again, but he’s different than last time..
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Mashiro and Monda`s Autumn Story
Mashiro to Monda no Aki Monogatari
ましろと紋田の秋物語
Mayoi o Koete: Mijuku na Hero!
Overcome Self-Doubt, Naive Hero!
迷いをこえて 未熟なヒーロー!

REGULAR.description:
Stuck in the middle of her new picture book, Mashiro goes to Sorashido Park. There, she meets Monda again and shows him her work in progress, but Monda gets angry…
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Prism Shine! Illuminate Your Heart
Prism Shine! Kokoro o Terashite!
プリズムシャイン! 心を照らして!

REGULAR.description:
Sora and the gang go to investigate a mysterious tunnel that appears in a Skyland field. There, they meet Empress Undergu, ruler of the Undergu Empire, who overpowers Cure Sky and the others with her immense power.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: A Grown-Up Princess and the Legendary Precure
Ookina Princess to Densetsu no Precure
大きなプリンセスと伝説のプリキュア
The Gentle Young Lady of the Undergu Empire
Undergu Teikoku no Yasashii Shoujo
アンダーグ帝国の優しい少女

REGULAR.description:
A Skyland event that resembles Christmas, it’s Strichmas! As they prepare to face off against the Undergu Empire, Sora and the others decide to hold a party to cheer everyone up.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Hero-tachi no Christmas
The Heroes` Christmas
ヒーローたちのクリスマス

REGULAR.description:
The Morning Star speaks to Ellee. It is revealed that the Morning Star was Elleelain all along and has been watching over Sora and the gang. Then, she gives the last of her power to Ellee.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Good-bye, Morning Star! The Princess Awakens!
Sayonara Ichibanboshi! Princess no Mezame!
さよなら一番星! プリンセスのめざめ!

REGULAR.description:
With the loss of Skearhead, the Empress burns with anger, and goes on a self-destructive mission. While the barrier is being destroyed, Cure Sky and the gang step up to protect the city.
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Heroes, Protect It! Everyone`s City!
Mamore Hero! Minna no Machi!
守れヒーロー! みんなの街!
Cure Sky and the Strongest Power
Cure Sky to Saikyou no Chikara
キュアスカイと最強の力

REGULAR.description:
Right after rescuing the Empress, Sky and the gang face a giant snake called Daijarg that emerges from the Sea of Undergu Energy. Unable to defeat Sky and the others, Daijarg escapes to…
Source: crunchyroll

titles.title: Mugen ni Hirogaru! Watashitachi no Sekai!
Soaring to Infinity! Our World!
無限にひろがる! わたしたちの世界!
